{"content":[{"id":"5e2016f4","settings":{"pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom"},"elements":[{"id":"5d6a58dc","settings":{"editor":"<p><!-- wp:html --><\/p>\n<p><img class=\"alignleft\" title=\"EMI-Logo-Yellow-Circle-No-Background-150-x-150\" src=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/EMI-Logo-Yellow-Circle-No-Background-150-x-150.png\" alt=\"EMI-Logo-Yellow-Circle-No-Background-150-x-150\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" \/> <img class=\"alignright\" title=\"1127e3b4-22d4-4916-be4d-60aa97338798-1583781551372\" src=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/1127e3b4-22d4-4916-be4d-60aa97338798-1583781551372.png\" alt=\"1127e3b4-22d4-4916-be4d-60aa97338798-1583781551372\" width=\"313\" height=\"80\" \/><\/p>\n<h1>Lochmueller Group: <br \/>Consulting 101 Webinar<a style=\"background-color: #ffffff; font-size: 21px;\" href=\"https:\/\/www.surveymonkey.com\/r\/Lochmueller-Consulting101Session\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\u00a0<\/a><iframe style=\"color: #3b3b3b; font-size: 21px; font-weight: 400;\" src=\"https:\/\/player.vimeo.com\/video\/859353399?h=27bc9e2ae0?badge=0&amp;autopause=0&amp;player_id=0&amp;app_id=58479\" width=\"640\" height=\"342\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"><\/iframe><\/h1>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/engineeringmanagementinstitute.org\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/09\/F-082923-Lochmueller-Consulting-101-v12.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Click Here to Download the Slides<\/a><\/p>\n<h3><i>Description:<\/i><\/h3>\n<p>This webinar given by Lochmueller leadership in partnership with the Engineering Management Institute (EMI) focused on an overview of consulting firms and how they operate with some specific items to Lochmueller, the business of consulting, and Lochmueller's values and growth opportunities now, and in the future. This session was also a kick-off to more professional development programs that will be coming at Lochmueller in the coming months focused around project management.\u00a0<\/p>\n<p><!-- \/wp:html --><\/p>","pa_condition_repeater":[],"premium_tooltip_text":"Hi, I'm a global tooltip.","premium_tooltip_position":"top,bottom","align":"center","align_widescreen":"center"},"elements":[],"isInner":false,"widgetType":"text-editor","elType":"widget"}],"isInner":false,"elType":"container"}],"settings":{"template":"default"},"metadata":{"_yoast_wpseo_estimated-reading-time-minutes":"1","_yoast_wpseo_content_score":"90","be_title_toggle_hide":"1","disable_sitewide_popup":"a:1:{i:0;s:4:\"true\";}","_yoast_wpseo_wordproof_timestamp":"","_yoast_wpseo_meta-robots-noindex":"1","_yoast_wpseo_meta-robots-nofollow":"1"}}